This technology uses a tension sensor such a load cell or dancer, to sense continuously the web tension directly measured in the material. The regulation for the tension is made by using a PID loop and is applied on the winder/unwinder speed.

Direct Power Control FB controls the manipulated variables output to a heating device. It is required to use combined with the PID control instruction having the MV tracking function. The Analog_DirPwrCtl FB gets both, fast reaction without overshoot.

This Function Block eliminates the machine vibration. It generates a target trajectory which does not occur resonance frequency vibration by continuous input from the command position. Maximum five different resonance vibrations can be suppressed at the same time.
